          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <placeName>Pittsburgh</placeName>
                                        <date>November the 10<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 5613</date>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">Revd Sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">The Occident this morning is come to hand I took
                                        notice<lb/> there, that your translation on the bible is all
                                        ready till<lb/> the first of <persName>Samuel</persName>, I
                                        hope you will <sic>recolect</sic> that <persName>Mr
                                                  Celner</persName><lb/> of
                                                  <placeName>Montgomery</placeName>, wrote once to
                                        you in my name, that I wish<lb/> to take one of them. I
                                        therefore beg of you, to be so kind as<lb/> to inform me
                                        about it every thing particularly I am very desirous<lb/>
                                        for it, if it is any thing to be done for you here, you have
                                        only to<lb/> command. I am with the greatest pleasure to
                                        your service<lb/> at any time. I hope I will soon be able to
                                        write in the<lb/> Occident, with the help of our God, I
                                        speak a great deal better<lb/> than I do write, but I hope
                                        in a short time to be able in writing<lb/> to, the five
                                        dollars I will send you please god with <persName>Mr<lb/>
                                                  Jaruslawsky</persName> as I have written.    I
                                        am</p>
                              <p rend="indent(10)">Sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">Your most <sic>respecfuly</sic> humble servt</p>
                              <p rend="indent(9)">
                                        <persName role="author">E. Marcuson</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p>have you any news?</p>
                              <p>I wrote this in great hurry. I have to go to the hospital, an
                                        Israelite is<lb/> there.</p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
